Abdomen (
Fig. 122
): All tergites with pair of broad irregular dark brown markings; mark on each tergite extended along posterior margin to lateral margin of tergite; markings on tergites 3–5 bi- or trimodal or with 1–2 small to large anterior yellow spots within them; markings broadly separated medially by slightly tapering, nearly straight margined yellow area.
